lastCommitMessage: Update version to 1.0.138 and refactor seller product management
- Updated version number and build details in version.json.
- Refactored seller product management routes, consolidating add and edit product pages into a unified product page.
- Enhanced navigation logic for improved user experience and removed deprecated pages.
- Added comprehensive form validation in SellerProductPage to ensure data integrity before submission.
- Improved image handling and display in product forms, including adaptive image widgets and error handling.
